name: Dorimaga GD Vol. 7
overview: Dorimaga GD Vol. 7 (ドリマガＧＤ Vol.7) is a Japanese Sega Dreamcast demo disc distributed with Dreamcast Magazine issue #2000-09-29. Playable Demos - DeSpiria, Outtrigger, 18 Wheeler: American Pro Trucker / Videos - Illbleed Trailer Movie, Capcom vs. SNK: Millennium Fight 2000 Special Movie
